    .section .text
    .global Azul6FactorySupply

    .include "Macros.asc"

Azul6FactorySupply:
; We can choose a tile from a factory or middle of table.
; we take all tiles of same type
; if it was a factory, other types on factory goto table.
; if you are the first taking from table, take the 1st player tile to floodline

; taken tiles must be put on a line (right to left)
; if tiles already there, type must match
; can't have 2 rows of same type.
; remaining tiles goto floodline

; repeat rotating players
; this phase is done when all factories and table are gone.

; functions needed
; - use selector to choose a tile from factory or table.
; - highlight that tile
; - use select to choose a line to put the tiles.
; - move 1stplayer tile
; - keep track of lines and floodline
; - comptuter AI
; - manage table??

